video.title: Mother Goose Club
video.synopsis: Classic nursery rhymes and children's songs get a fresh twist in this high-energy program that helps kids learn as they dance and sing along.

episodes.synopsis: Join the Mother Goose Club and dance to 20 of their favorite tunes, including "Five Little Monkeys," "Dinosaur Stomp" and "Driving in My Car."
episodes.title: Jump Up and Rhyme with Mother Goose Club

episodes.synopsis: The club sings, laughs and learns with their favorite cartoons, including "Soccer Rocker," "ABC Song with Eep the Mouse" and "Baa Baa Black Sheep."
episodes.title: Mother Goose Club Presents Classic Cartoons

episodes.synopsis: The club welcomes their friend Jack B. Nimble, who leads the gang in "Rockin' Robot," "The Wheels on the Bus," "Swimming" and other dances.
episodes.title: Mother Goose Club Presents Jack B. Nimble

episodes.synopsis: The Mother Goose Club friends laugh and learn with "Ten Little Dinosaurs, "Three Little Kittens," "Wheels on the Bus" and other favorite cartoons.
episodes.title: Mother Goose Club Presents the Wheels on the Bus and More Cartoons!

episodes.synopsis: The kids of the Mother Goose Club sing and dance to favorites like "Old MacDonald," "Bingo," "Muffin Man," "One Potato, Two Potato" and dozens more.
episodes.title: Mother Goose Club Presents Rhyme with Us
